{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "不出一月，天目山藏有绝世美人与巨万金珠神兵的消息传遍武林，各路豪杰纷纷赶往临安。临安城龙门居茶馆中，秃鹰殷老五向峨嵋弟子杨振引见多臂神剑云谦、仁义剑客云中程父子。杨振傲慢无礼，拂袖而去。入夜后，雁荡红巾会惨遭灭门，号角四起，血迹满街。云中程循血迹追踪至城外，发现红巾会总瓢把子丁红巾重伤垂死，未能说出仇家即气绝。火场中两名红裳少女现身抢夺一粒红珠后离去。一位玄衫少年从容步出火海，云中程认出他是亡父挚友中原大侠卓浩然之子卓长卿。卓长卿含泪告知双亲十年前在黄山始信峰下遭人毒手。二人回到龙门居，多臂神剑见到故人之子悲喜交加，卓长卿为免老人伤心隐瞒噩耗。云中程讲述红巾会覆灭之事，多臂神剑感叹武林多事，而卓长卿此行正是为寻仇而来。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": "char_yang_zhen",
      "text": "不是我殷老五在灭自己的威风，可是那天那个一身黄衫的少年朋友，手底下可真有两下子，连管神鹰那种角色，不出三招，就认栽服输。杨老弟，你的一手峨嵋剑法，虽然使得漂亮，但比起人家来——嘿，还差着好大一截哩。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "杨振",
      "listener": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "text": "殷五哥既然这么说，想必不会差的了。但是，殷五哥，你可知道，别的地方不说，就在这临安城里，扎手的角色，少说也有十个，雁荡红巾会、太行快刀会的总瓢把子，这次竟也都亲自来了。你说的这个姓岑的少年朋友，虽然手把子硬，但这次想压倒群雄，独占鳌头，只怕也不可能吧？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": "char_yang_zhen",
      "text": "这可也说不定。杨老弟，你是没有赶上那场热闹。要是那天你也在场的话，你就会知道，我殷老五说的话不是乱打高空了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "云老爷子，你老人家也来了呀。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "text": "这位兄弟是谁？小弟倒面生得很。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云大哥，今天让小弟给你引见一位成名露脸的朋友。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": "char_yang_zhen",
      "text": "杨老弟，你可知道，坐在你对面的，就是名满天下的多臂神剑云老爷子，和仁义剑客云大哥。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位杨老弟，就是峨嵋派的掌门弟子，扬名蜀中的杨一剑杨振。哈哈，想不到你们二位居然没有会过面，更想不到今天我殷老五能够引见你们二位。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_yang_zhen",
      "text": "老夫早就听得峨嵋静波上人有个出类拔萃的弟子，今日一见，气宇果自不凡。故人绝技得传，真叫老夫高兴得很。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "杨振",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "老前辈过奖了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "殷五爷哪里交来这么好的朋友！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "中程，你的涵养到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yin_lao_wu",
      "speaker_name": "秃鹰殷老五",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "红巾号。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雁荡红巾会，怎会在这临安城里开起坛来？难道红巾三豪，此刻全都到了临安城吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "仁义剑客",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "爹爹，您老人家在此稍微歇一歇，我出去看看。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "仁义剑客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是怎么回事？你们怎样受的伤？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "黑衣大汉",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "好狠的心……好狠的心……我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "杨一剑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云大侠驰马狂奔，是否也是为着惨呼之声？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_yang_zhen",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "杨一剑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云大侠要去，那好极了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_ding_hong_jin",
      "text": "丁兄，你可还认识小弟？方才……这桩事，究竟是谁干出来的？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_ding_hong_jin",
      "text": "是不是快刀会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_ding_hong_jin",
      "text": "是不是黑米帮？……哦……难道是太湖三十六寨吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两河那边的天阴教，和丁兄也结有梁子吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "左侧红裳少女",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "我当是谁呢，原来是云少侠。您怎么也来了？您看，这颗小珠子多好玩，是您的吗？送给我们姐妹两个好不好？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "text": "多日未见，两位姑娘越发娇艳了。这种鲜血淋漓的地方，两位怎么也有兴趣前来呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "左侧红裳少女",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云少侠，您不说这珠子是不是您的，我们可就要收下了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chui_tiao_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "右侧红裳少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "云少侠，您看这个丫头脸皮厚不厚，随便在地上捡起一样东西，居然就算是自己的了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "左侧红裳少女",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "你呢！你刚才不是也和我在抢，现在没有抢到，就眼红了是不是？云少侠，我告诉你，普天之下，就数她的脸皮最厚了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "text": "这粒珠子，虽非在下所有之物，但却——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "text": "是自然应该归两位所有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "左侧红裳少女",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "谢谢您啦——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红裳少女",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云少侠，我们走了，过两天我们再下山来拜谒云老爷子，请您回去代我们向他老人家问好。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫少年",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "小可冒昧，阁下想必就是仁义剑客云中程云大侠吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫少年",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "小弟初入江湖，对武林侠踪，虽然生疏得很，但云大侠手中的这柄比寻常剑短了六寸，却比寻常剑锋利百倍的龙纹软剑，小弟却早就从先父和家师口中听到过，是以小弟一见此剑，便猜出阁下定必就是仁义剑客了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "玄衫少年",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "云大哥，你难道不记得，十余年前，那缠在你身边求你传授两招云门剑法的长卿了吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "原来你就是长卿弟！十年不见，可想死哥哥我了。长卿弟，你怎么也来到这里了？这十年来，你都到哪里去了？老伯他可好吗？唉——岁月如梭，长卿弟，你已出落得一表人材，又有一身绝技，可是——哥哥我却已老了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿弟，你怎么了，难道……难道老伯……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "大哥，我爹爹和……我妈妈，在十年以前，就……在黄山……始信峰下，遭……遭了别人……的毒手了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "大哥，你带我去见见老伯吧。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿弟，等一会。你见了爹爹，千万不要将老伯的噩耗对他老人家说出来。他老人家……年龄大了，恐怕……恐怕受不了……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "是中程吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "text": "中程，你可看到什么吗？怎么去了这么久？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "爹爹，你老人家猜猜看，这位少年英雄是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，你是不是长卿？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "老伯，小侄正是长卿，十年来……老伯精神越发瞿铄。",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "云谦",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "快起来，快起来——",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "想不到，想不到，你也长得这么高大了。你爹爹呢？怎么也不来看看我这老头子，难道他已把我给忘了吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "家父他老人家……这些年……都没有出来，特地叫小侄问候您老人家好。",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "好，好，这么多年都没有出来，老朋友是什么东西，只要他卓大爷住得舒服就成了——",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "孩子，不要吃惊，我……我只是想你爹爹，想得太厉害了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "老伯，你老人家是家父的知己，唉——家父实是有难言的苦衷，你老人家不会见怪吧？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，我和你爹爹数十年过命的交情，还有什么见怪不见怪的？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "来，告诉我，你是怎么也来到这里的，又是怎么遇着中程的？这些年来，想必你已从你爹爹那里学得了一身功夫，此刻倒是你一展身手的机会了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，你心中若有忧郁之事，不妨说给我听听。此刻你既然已离开了你的爹爹，不妨——就将我看做你的爹爹一样……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，你这是怎么了？有什么事只管说出来，老夫拼却性命，也得为你做主。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "老伯，小侄……",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 604
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "speaker_name": "卓长卿",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "小侄离开了爹爹以后——",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿，究竟是怎么回事——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "长卿弟想必是离家口久，心里有了些难受。不过，长卿弟，此刻你既然已来到这里，我却要多留你一些日子了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "此刻这临安城里，不但风云际会，群豪毕至，而且怪异之事，层出不穷，贤弟若没有来，我还真不知道如何是好哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 620
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_zhong_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "云中程",
      "listener": "char_yun_qian",
      "text": "雁荡红巾会，崛起江湖的时日虽短，但会中人手却极整齐，势力并非等闲，哪知今日却在这临安城里一败涂地。此事不仅奇怪，而且简直有些不可思议。试想能将这红巾会一举而灭的人，又该是如何人物呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_qian",
      "speaker_name": "多臂神剑",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_chang_qing",
      "text": "自从那天老夫眼见万妙真君和红衣娘娘的传人一齐出现，老夫就知道，芸芸武林，必定又将多事。长卿——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 632
    }
  ],
